      "#kitchenpickleball",
      "#pickleballaddict",
      "#pickleballcommunity"
    ],
    "ron_burgundy_voice": "Well, it appears we have a rather... *vigorous* exchange of small, yellow balls happening over there. It's a real testament to the human spirit, I suppose. They're just... hitting them. Back and forth. Fascinating. Truly. Stay classy, pickleball fans.",
    "chuck_norris_voice": "Chuck Norris doesn't play pickleball; pickleball plays itself when Chuck Norris is on the court.",
    "color_commentator_banter": "You know, I've seen some dink battles in my day, but this one is something special. It's like a chess match, but with paddles and a ball. I'm just waiting for one of them to make a move, you know? Like a surprise attack, a little drop shot, something to shake things up!",
    "crowd_chant_if_epic": "DINK! DINK! DINK! DINK!",
    "trash_talk_friendly": "Alright, let's see if you can keep that up all day! My patience is wearing thin!",
